caption:
A beautiful evening at the National Portrait Gallery celebrating the MUNCH x Rejina Pyo collaboration.

Guests enjoyed a private viewing of the Edvard Munch: Portraits exhibition, followed by an intimate conversation between Rejina Pyo and artist Allison Katz, moderated by art critic Louisa Buck. The evening was hosted in collaboration with the Munch Museum and Hauser & Wirth, and concluded with dinner at the Portrait Restaurant, overlooking Trafalgar Square. 
⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
Thank you to everyone who joined us and made it so special.
